!theme plain
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam nodesep 80
skinparam ranksep 80

' --- STYLING (HIMS Blue Theme) ---
skinparam class {
 BackgroundColor #436FB6
 FontColor white
 ArrowColor #2F528F
 BorderColor #2F528F
 FontSize 14
 AttributeFontSize 12
 MethodFontSize 12
}
skinparam arrow {
 Color #2F528F
 FontColor #444444
}

' --- CLASSES ---

abstract class \"User\" {
 + userID: String {PK}
 + email: String
 + passwordHash: String
 + fullName: String
 + createdAt: DateTime
 __
 + login(): Boolean
 + logout(): Void
 + resetPassword(): Void
}

class \"Driver\" {
 + driverID: String
 + licenseNumber: String
 + shiftStatus: Enum {ON_DUTY, OFF_DUTY}
 + currentBusID: String {FK}
 __
 + startTrip(routeID: String): Boolean
 + stopTrip(): Boolean
 + broadcastGPS(lat: Float, lng: Float): Void
}

class \"Passenger\" {
 + passengerID: String
 + preferences: JSON
 __
 + searchRoute(query: String): List<Route>
 + viewLiveMap(busID: String): MapView
 + getETA(stopID: String): Time
}

class \"Admin\" {
 + adminID: String
 + permissions: List<String>
 __
 + addBus(busDetails: Bus): Boolean
 + removeBus(busID: String): Boolean
 + updateRoute(routeDetails: Route): Void
 + viewSystemLogs(): List<Log>
}

class \"Bus\" {
 + busID: String {PK}
 + plateNumber: String
 + capacity: Integer
 + status: Enum {ACTIVE, MAINTENANCE, IDLE}
 + currentLat: Float
 + currentLng: Float
 __
 + updateLocation(lat: Float, lng: Float): Void
 + assignDriver(driverID: String): Void
}

class \"Route\" {
 + routeID: String {PK}
 + routeName: String
 + totalDistance: Float
 + googlePolyline: String
 __
 + addStop(stop: Stop): Void
 + calculateTotalTime(): Time
}

class \"Stop\" {
 + stopID: String {PK}
 + name: String
 + latitude: Float
 + longitude: Float
 __
 + getCoordinates(): Coordinate
}

class \"Notification\" {
 + notificationID: String
 + recipientID: String {FK}
 + message: String
 + timestamp: DateTime
 __
 + sendPushAlert(): Void
}

' --- RELATIONSHIPS ---

' Inheritance
User <|-- Driver
User <|-- Passenger
User <|-- Admin

' Associations
Driver \"1\" --> \"0..1\" Bus : \"Drives >\"
Bus \"1\" --> \"1\" Route : \"Operates On >\"
Route \"1\" *-- \"1..*\" Stop : \"Composed Of >\"
Bus \"1\" --> \"0..*\" Notification : \"Triggers Alert >\"
Passenger \"1\" ..> \"0..*\" Notification : \"Receives >\"
